ectron microscope.</gtr:description><gtr:id>4E5B9149-D523-4954-9E18-4751A0886BA2</gtr:id><gtr:impact>This technology is being introduced into the Ionscope range of scanning ion conductance microscopes, which will make this UK-based SEM more competitive in the global market.</gtr:impact><gtr:providedToOthers>true</gtr:providedToOthers><gtr:title>A method for estimating the geometry of SICM probes</gtr:title><gtr:type>Technology assay or reagent</gtr:type><gtr:yearFirstProvided>2012</gtr:yearFirstProvided></gtr:researchMaterialOutput></gtr:researchMaterialOutputs><gtr:softwareAndTechnicalProductOutputs/><gtr:spinOutOutputs/></gtr:output><gtr:publications><gtr:publication url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/publication/A973957C-578B-40BA-A830-127A2089028D"><gtr:id>A973957C-578B-40BA-A830-127A2089028D</gtr:id><gtr:title>Contact-free scanning and imaging with the scanning ion conductance microscope.</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>Analytical chemistry</gtr:parentPublicationTitle><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/person/41baf6cdde6cf6762ed2546ff751c16a"><gtr:id>41baf6cdde6cf6762ed2546ff751c16a</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>Del Linz S</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2014-01-01</gtr:date><gtr:issn>0003-2700</gtr:issn></gtr:publication><gtr:publication url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/publication/E7CA0207-4889-4A63-95AC-748230A94560"><gtr:id>E7CA0207-4889-4A63-95AC-748230A94560</gtr:id><gtr:title>Nanoscale live-cell imaging using hopping probe ion conductance microscopy.</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>Nature methods</gtr:parentPublicationTitle><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/person/f5c74f2f031a8194794fe50f22d63d5c"><gtr:id>f5c74f2f031a8194794fe50f22d63d5c</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>Novak P</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2009-01-01</gtr:date><gtr:issn>1548-7091</gtr:issn></gtr:publication><gtr:publication url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/publication/3B635252-7516-4D03-A10F-5DA8FB661AFE"><gtr:id>3